   <ul style="text-align: justify;">
    <li><b>Custom Tattoos:</b>Our team of talented tattoo artists specializes in bringing your ideas to life. We work closely with you to design a one-of-a-kind tattoo that perfectly represents your style, story, or sentiment.</li>
    <li><b>Cover-Up Tattoos:</b>If you have an old or unwanted tattoo, we can help you transform it into a new masterpiece. Our artists excel in cover-up tattoos, expertly concealing the past while creating a fresh, beautiful design.</li>
    <li><b>Flash Tattoos:</b>For those looking for smaller, ready-made designs, we offer a wide selection of flash tattoos. These designs are perfect for spontaneous expressions of creativity or as an introduction to the world of body art.</li>
    <li><b>Tattoo Aftercare:</b>At Kavya beauty parlour, we are committed to your well-being. We provide thorough guidance on tattoo aftercare, ensuring your new ink heals beautifully and maintains its vibrancy.</li>
   </ul>
   <h4>The Kavya Experience:</h4>
   <ul style="text-align: justify;">
    <li><b>Talented Artists:</b> Our team of tattoo artists is comprised of skilled professionals who are passionate about their craft. Each artist has their own unique style, allowing us to cater to a diverse range of preferences.</li>
    <li><b>Safety and Hygiene: </b>Your health and safety are our top priorities. We follow strict hygiene and sterilization protocols to ensure that your tattoo experience is not only enjoyable but also safe.</li>
